Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.09,0:00:12.86,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独自一人 试着来到 往日的公园
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.95,0:00:16.58,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A feeling never felt
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.59,0:00:22.27,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像个孩子似的 惧怕着风的声响
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.27,0:00:25.61,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奔跑在回家的路上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.13,0:00:34.56,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窗户之外 是太过宽广的天空 where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.87,0:00:36.40,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传达给你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.77,0:00:44.64,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这愿望若某天能够实现的话 呐 神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.19,0:00:50.14,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就帮我实现吧 my wish
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.81,0:00:56.31,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要听见你的声音 miss you 想要见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.58,0:01:00.82,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论怎样 都在看着明天吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.30,0:01:06.45,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要放跑 timing 不要说得这么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.45,0:01:08.70,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要再一次
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.17,0:01:14.80,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明最喜欢你 it's too late 从很久以前起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.94,0:01:19.52,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使放弃 也无法回到过去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.53,0:01:24.84,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有办法 no way 不要简单地下结论
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.86,0:01:28.75,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}只要再 笑一次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.49,0:22:35.93,ed_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要互相了解 将真心话互相诉诸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.94,0:22:42.11,ed_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有你的眼泪 也有你的笑颜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.20,0:22:49.63,ed_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论怎样的苦痛也不再害怕 两个人话无论哪里都能去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.62,0:22:54.96,ed_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你告诉了我 我不是独自一人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.97,0:23:03.22,ed_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我生在世上只为见你 每当我试着轻语这句话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.25,0:23:08.07,ed_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不安便消失不见 心中亮起坚强之光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.09,0:23:15.34,ed_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢之意只有你我知晓 随着信号我们共同前进
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.33,0:23:20.52,ed_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将无法替代的时刻 铭刻于心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.97,0:23:28.78,ed_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法从这个地方离去 感受着同样的悸动活着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.80,0:23:33.48,ed_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一再许诺的约定 想要将其彻底履行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.49,0:23:40.81,ed_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢之意只有你我知晓 随着信号我们共同前进
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.82,0:23:46.69,ed_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}将无法替代的时刻 铭刻于心

Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.14,0:01:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米纳米博士？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.97,0:01:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 是那个开口说出要停下斯库拉古的球体的那个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.48,0:01:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 米纳米博士是在协助NIA捕获GHOST对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.58,0:01:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 但是他利用其立场掌握了军方的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.64,0:01:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.94,0:01:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立马察觉到的修兹虽然想要挽回事态
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.29,0:02:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在米纳米失去了控制
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.42,0:02:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我来介绍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.33,0:02:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是活艺术
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.45,0:02:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MR-1
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.42,0:02:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MR-1?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.05,0:02:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的 我知道的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.28,0:02:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的弱点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.96,0:02:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有装备远距离攻击用的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.19,0:02:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不接近你的格斗范围 就毫无问题
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.66,0:02:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HEROMAN…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.89,0:02:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.46,0:02:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米纳米博士 立即投降
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.99,0:02:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗到此已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.42,0:02:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊我知道了 如你所说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.94,0:02:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来战斗就结束了

Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.48,0:03:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第16话    决定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.48,0:03:08.36,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Decision

Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.56,0:03:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HEROMAN被…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.64,0:03:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做到了 终于做到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.68,0:03:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来就证明了我的MR-1是宇宙最强
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.72,0:03:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来能对抗我的发明的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.49,0:03:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.03,0:03:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.70,0:03:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HEROMAN的力量之源是电力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.67,0:04:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个夜晚HEROMAN是因雷击而诞生的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.38,0:04:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前为止的招数全部都陆续使用了电的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.63,0:04:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管多么强大的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.21,0:04:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那是电的力量的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.57,0:04:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HEROMAN就没有被打倒的可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.13,0:04:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HEROMAN
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.84,0:04:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.07,0:04:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.34,0:04:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个距离 是HEROMAN的距离！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.65,0:04:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.07,0:04:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HEROMAN
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.05,0:04:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迅速脱离
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.73,0:05:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎能让你逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HEROMAN
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.02,0:05:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Magnet！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.55,0:05:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少得意了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.59,0:05:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干掉了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.56,0:05:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.50,0:06:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来便不会再让你拉开距离了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.53,0:06:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也好 我就接下你的挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你所得意的格斗战中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.29,0:06:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将你轰至体无完肤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能将MR-1的胜利突显得更加美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.67,0:06:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一决胜负 GHOST
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.07,0:06:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米纳米博士 你可以适可而止了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.82,0:06:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻终止战斗并投降
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投降？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.07,0:06:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了 你将被判以叛国罪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.11,0:06:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.85,0:06:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装傻也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.40,0:07:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我做好觉悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.64,0:07:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那还真是抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.91,0:07:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我会这么说吗！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.77,0:07:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米纳米 你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.74,0:07:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通信到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.42,0:07:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要稍微让你们闭一会嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.93,0:07:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘书
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.14,0:07:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.77,0:07:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 全机紧急回避
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修兹先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.86,0:07:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么 快点稳定住直升机
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.33,0:07:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 电子仪器全部无法使用了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.35,0:07:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是那个导弹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.81,0:07:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 虽然对GHOST可能无效但对你们那是效果显著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.15,0:07:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 没了碍事的人就让我尽情干一番吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.34,0:08:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看 是烟尘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.90,0:08:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 看来还没结束
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.17,0:08:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 是不是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.12,0:08:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.03,0:08:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我拉住你团团转
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.31,0:08:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是根电磁锁链别以为能赢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.71,0:08:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位观众 你们是否看见了这场面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.99,0:08:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此画面是由All American Network带来的世纪性的大头条
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.72,0:08:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天在媒体中引起轰动的迷之地球外生命体——通称GHOST
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.66,0:09:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和以军事目的而制造的机器人正展开着激烈的死斗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.13,0:09:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.47,0:09:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会 现在应该已对报道进行了管制
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.40,0:09:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是电视台？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.45,0:09:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媒体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.64,0:09:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.57,0:09:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我在众目睽睽之下将你大卸八块
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.15,0:09:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请看 那架直升机下方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.00,0:09:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是机器人工学的权威 米纳米博士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.27,0:09:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.36,0:09:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个有着巨大双臂的机器人应该便是米纳米博士开发的MR-1
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.29,0:09:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MR-1曾为了停下斯库拉古的球体因军方要求出动过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在使用力量的几秒前球体自然停止
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.13,0:09:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后辗转于Center City的重建支援工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.44,0:09:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这台机器人现在又被再次订造
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.46,0:09:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猛烈地狂飙着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.02,0:10:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其对抗的GHOST则时常出没于Center City帮助重建工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.36,0:10:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在市民之间被传为正义的我方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.52,0:10:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是以某条新闻为分界线 传言转而变得充满否定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 那条新闻便是一则关于袭击重建设施的报道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.07,0:10:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被这么牵着到处跑不论我还是HEROMAN都受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.36,0:10:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么做

Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.34,0:11:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞到了个很有趣的地方嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.81,0:11:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在这里一决胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.64,0:11:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃吧 逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.31,0:11:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可未必一直会有立足点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.30,0:11:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.73,0:11:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HEROMAN
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.92,0:11:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔伊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修兹先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.49,0:11:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的伤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.54,0:11:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意 轻伤而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.08,0:11:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 以我的力量没能阻止米纳米
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.81,0:11:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这样一来再也不会被军方敌对了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.19,0:11:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这全多亏了修兹先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.04,0:11:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来米纳米的脑子里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.18,0:11:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经只剩下用自己的机器人打败HEROMAN这事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.84,0:11:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米纳米为了让MR1被军队正式采用进行了种种策动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.11,0:12:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽在与斯库拉古的战斗中被HEROMAN抢先了一步
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.40,0:12:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但打倒那个消灭了斯库拉古的HEROMAN的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.82,0:12:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便会成为恰好不过的宣言材料
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.11,0:12:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此才把HEROMAN当成坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.12,0:12:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 但是不止如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.96,0:12:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于夺走自己活跃时机的HEROMAN一直怀狠于心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.44,0:12:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.57,0:12:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔伊 不 乔瑟夫·卡特·琼斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.22,0:12:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一事相求
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.41,0:12:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来自大总统直属机关NIA的正式请求
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.14,0:12:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去阻止暴走了的米纳米
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.93,0:12:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在损害继续扩大前 希望你们能破坏掉MR1
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.83,0:12:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.80,0:12:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HEROMAN
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.51,0:12:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.88,0:13:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,压你个稀巴烂！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.65,0:13:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.75,0:13:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.07,0:13:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HEROMAN
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.81,0:13:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HEROMAN
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.90,0:13:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉..掉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.99,0:13:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HEROMAN 现在立刻就来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.70,0:13:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.11,0:13:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会 能量…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.62,0:13:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底为什么会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.35,0:14:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 乔伊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.97,0:14:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修兹先生 有事拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.65,0:14:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来GHOST似乎没事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.90,0:14:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MR-1仍沉在水中 毫无气息
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.61,0:14:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来胜负已定了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.22,0:14:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米纳米博士那边 从刚才开始就保持着沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.46,0:14:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受损部位检查
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.16,0:14:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平衡器再检查
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.57,0:14:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,备用动力启动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.35,0:14:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MR-1 重启
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.86,0:15:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.42,0:15:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗再次开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.78,0:15:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.22,0:15:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙啊乔伊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.70,0:15:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大坝！大坝的墙面因MR1的攻击开始崩坏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.82,0:15:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了 这样下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.94,0:15:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HEROMAN
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.69,0:15:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这..这是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.49,0:15:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GHOST开始挡住MR-1的刺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.66,0:16:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然小看人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.19,0:16:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算保住了大坝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.17,0:16:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死的还是得死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.09,0:16:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HEROMAN
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.92,0:16:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.50,0:16:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔伊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.90,0:16:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米纳米博士在想些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.06,0:16:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大坝被摧毁的话 明显会对下游的居民造成甚大的受害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.15,0:16:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 米纳米博士制造的兵器继续着毫不留情的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.58,0:16:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来被世人贴上恶之标签的GHOST
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.35,0:16:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却为了保护大坝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.77,0:16:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拼命地努力着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.80,0:16:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是完全未经编辑的直播影像
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.83,0:16:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位看着这影像是何心情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.09,0:16:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.82,0:16:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他并不是威胁着人类的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.40,0:16:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他才正是保护着我们如同盾牌般的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.65,0:16:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他才正是我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.01,0:17:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的hero
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.54,0:17:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 没子弹了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.24,0:17:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后一击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.92,0:17:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎..怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.83,0:17:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔伊 这下发电设施应该就处于全开状态了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.11,0:17:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.03,0:17:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 这样真的可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.94,0:17:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HEROMAN也是要吃午饭的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.25,0:17:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发电设施
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.15,0:18:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙 这很不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.47,0:18:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HEROMAN
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.65,0:18:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Attack！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.25,0:18:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.14,0:19:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,障眼法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.32,0:19:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢货 就算从上方看不见 MR-1也装载着眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.24,0:19:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.36,0:19:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米纳米博士 在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.15,0:19:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HEROMAN
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.89,0:19:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blast！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.27,0:20:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做到了 GHOST的完全胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.02,0:20:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.17,0:20:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英雄大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.53,0:21:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样 我们的逃亡之旅结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.38,0:21:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全靠修兹先生 我们洗清冤名无罪释放
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.22,0:21:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在随后的电视现场直播中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.60,0:21:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知何时起 将HEROMAN从坏蛋捧为了正义的我方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.10,0:21:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无可奉告 无可奉告
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.43,0:21:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疯狂科学家·米纳米博士和他的同伙则…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.07,0:21:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样我们又回到了一直以来的日常中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.02,0:21:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔伊 能再来杯咖啡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.03,0:21:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.83,0:21:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.00,0:21:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟乔伊 还是老样子呐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.72,0:21:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修兹先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.80,0:22:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来杯咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.07,0:22:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是

Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.31,0:23:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回的heroman讲述的是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.52,0:23:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自由真的是最棒的了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.83,0:23:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平第一
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.41,0:23:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃亡剧终了的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.49,0:24:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔伊一行享受了刹那间的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.73,0:24:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 在那背后新的事件发生了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.87,0:24:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在乔伊一行面前现身的意外人物
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.91,0:24:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他发出了警告
